{"tid":483820,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"用foobar2000嘅你點入歌落iPhone","createTime":"2017-11-29T13:21:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T13:57:44.000Z","uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c934355fcdfb83da935e279f758002892f1877e3","tid":483820,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T13:21:28.000Z","msg":"我淨係想Copy某幾個Playlists嘅歌去iPhone (iOS 11)<br />\n但係好似只可以經iTunes直接Copy啲folder過去<br />\n例如成個Artist或者某個Album嘅folder<br />\n<br />\n有冇方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ff929d7786556dcac3de5056783074795ed67c","tid":483820,"uid":3765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:19:20.000Z","msg":"支那野<br />\n<br />\niTools 3  唔好用新版"},{"pid":"d7ddf19cf9d12b5554a7e28f8ebba9bd77290552","tid":483820,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T15:24:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那野<br />\n<br />\niTools 3  唔好用新版</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03dde7dfad7d183696b0590ddbfa0c2494eac0ba","tid":483820,"uid":23094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T16:38:39.000Z","msg":"講漏咗, 有啲歌係FLAC/Hi-Res<br />\n所以應該唔可以用返原本個Music app嚟聽<br />\n有咩App係入歌方便啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a03c2909cdccb1883873e3fc6dc163aa2c6649f","tid":483820,"uid":6677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T02:51:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講漏咗, 有啲歌係FLAC/Hi-Res<br />\n所以應該唔可以用返原本個Music app嚟聽<br />\n有咩App係入歌方便啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正正經經買部player啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3cc93441232949bd0a173d2c6e52498e136471a","tid":483820,"uid":48491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T06:00:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講漏咗, 有啲歌係FLAC/Hi-Res<br />\n所以應該唔可以用返原本個Music app嚟聽<br />\n有咩App係入歌方便啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n將FLAC嘅轉晒做ALAC<br />\n採樣頻率大過48KHz嘅Hi-Res全部降採樣做48KHz<br />\n咁就可以用返原生Music App<br />\n<br />\n利申：只係得部5S，唔知新機係咪已經可以支緩其它格式"},{"pid":"f0918f3c5a6ba3c88c4127d6b30d6c9116a9ce9c","tid":483820,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T07:49:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講漏咗, 有啲歌係FLAC/Hi-Res<br />\n所以應該唔可以用返原本個Music app嚟聽<br />\n有咩App係入歌方便啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正正經經買部player啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當年買咗Seiun Pro X，點知到而家都仲未出貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n\b等個孫幫我收貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac26f526e0def3269ca0eb9170d59b998b6cb4c3","tid":483820,"uid":18641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T10:37:30.000Z","msg":"同問<br />\nItunes 好唔方便"},{"pid":"45b97c8b39047e7494ed03ebd6fc46e434c5fe4d","tid":483820,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T10:58:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同問<br />\nItunes 好唔方便</blockquote><br />\n其實入歌落手機嚟講係幾方便<br />\n但係喺電腦用就好唔方便，啲Metadata好多都唔清唔楚<br />\n有時以為佢Save咗個Tag，但係用第2個Software開個File睇原來係冇嘅<br />\n我懷疑可能只係Save咗落個Library file<br />\n仲要到2018都仲係唔Support FLAC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\niTunes Store買歌係方便，但係都係未有得買Lossless<br />\n最大優點我諗係得Smart Playlist同埋Sync嘢落手機<br />\n但係而家連App Store都閹埋，真係唔知仲用佢嚟做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"818e0d035c6c468567309444f12d3c4473e08157","tid":483820,"uid":5711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T14:49:19.000Z","msg":"foobar 有ios version<br />\n直接用itune drag flac 落foobar 就聽得"},{"pid":"b9968802205f1b60d561ea2d7529df0072adb1f5","tid":483820,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T20:20:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>foobar 有ios version<br />\n直接用itune drag flac 落foobar 就聽得</blockquote><br />\n我一開始就試咗呢個<br />\n就係覺得只可以成個Folder咁搬唔夠方便<br />\n想有啲Tools可以判斷某幾個Playlists加埋有邊啲歌<br />\n最好可以放埋Playlist入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afbbbf8f27ea730152432bb89991e4b7eecc97f4","tid":483820,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T21:37:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce431369483b50de61fe3bcec2b67d090701902e","tid":483820,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T17:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac139237e3925b19c05c48966b17f4d3f2e2e0d0","tid":483820,"uid":136527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T17:38:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51fb52c967310ad18acc9dcc510448b8831db07e","tid":483820,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T17:55:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推</blockquote><br />\n同道中人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a030151c03d3db79a2f59ef5f8d8fe6847862b3a","tid":483820,"uid":136527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:08:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>推</blockquote><br />\n同道中人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nth same <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4908863ed0d21dfc9d94965c31189309bc2765","tid":483820,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T15:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c837acdf53594eea21167ebd552dfe9418f2fa5f","tid":483820,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T15:56:41.000Z","msg":"唔用iphone<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a2641513500dbc49c622524b610811ef364aff","tid":483820,"uid":6677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T01:10:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同問<br />\nItunes 好唔方便</blockquote><br />\n其實入歌落手機嚟講係幾方便<br />\n但係喺電腦用就好唔方便，啲Metadata好多都唔清唔楚<br />\n有時以為佢Save咗個Tag，但係用第2個Software開個File睇原來係冇嘅<br />\n我懷疑可能只係Save咗落個Library file<br />\n仲要到2018都仲係唔Support FLAC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\niTunes Store買歌係方便，但係都係未有得買Lossless<br />\n最大優點我諗係得Smart Playlist同埋Sync嘢落手機<br />\n但係而家連App Store都閹埋，真係唔知仲用佢嚟做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩format?wav的確係無id3 tag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e86621b7a0e89769293f34dfaa48130aba1f006","tid":483820,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T11:15:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同問<br />\nItunes 好唔方便</blockquote><br />\n其實入歌落手機嚟講係幾方便<br />\n但係喺電腦用就好唔方便，啲Metadata好多都唔清唔楚<br />\n有時以為佢Save咗個Tag，但係用第2個Software開個File睇原來係冇嘅<br />\n我懷疑可能只係Save咗落個Library file<br />\n仲要到2018都仲係唔Support FLAC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\niTunes Store買歌係方便，但係都係未有得買Lossless<br />\n最大優點我諗係得Smart Playlist同埋Sync嘢落手機<br />\n但係而家連App Store都閹埋，真係唔知仲用佢嚟做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩format?wav的確係無id3 tag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAIFF"},{"pid":"c4d69574774db60e97bbef650748bdf6900215ea","tid":483820,"uid":6677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:53:32.000Z","msg":"Aiff好似都係無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844691b6535a574f8a5e0c04cab13b850bb5aa2a","tid":483820,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:58:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Aiff好似都係無